            "title": "天文台｜最高氣溫約29度 稍後及今晚驟雨逐漸增多 部分地區雨勢較大",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/ca88ff917b78ba05e486f899537e04b8/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250510/_2025051007100493529.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">蔡楚輝攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>廣東沿岸風勢微弱。同時，華中的氣壓正在上升，預料一道冷鋒今日會在華南北部形成，並在今晚橫過沿岸地區。\n\n</p>\n<p>本港地區今日大致多雲，有幾陣驟雨。早上部分時間天色明朗。最高氣溫約29度。日間稍後及今晚驟雨逐漸增多及有幾陣狂風雷暴，部分地區雨勢較大。吹微風，晚上北風增強，氣溫逐步下降至午夜最低約23度。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4240416/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"日間稍後及今晚驟雨逐漸增多及有幾陣狂風雷暴，部分地區雨勢較大。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cbdf6683e2da040e5778f60ed12325df/2025-05/4_0_1.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        日間稍後及今晚驟雨逐漸增多及有幾陣狂風雷暴，部分地區雨勢較大。蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4240417/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5cda3c7631a664692009367f76422def/2025-05/Screenshot_2025-05-10_at_12_03_35_AM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"me