ary-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        日間稍後及今晚驟雨逐漸增多及有幾陣狂風雷暴，部分地區雨勢較大。蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4240421/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"日間稍後及今晚驟雨逐漸增多及有幾陣狂風雷暴，部分地區雨勢較大。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/02d2cf72c37c79485d0308b9ff437c59/2025-05/2_10.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        日間稍後及今晚驟雨逐漸增多及有幾陣狂風雷暴，部分地區雨勢較大。蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4240422/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"本港地區今日大致多雲，有幾陣驟雨。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/48916b9c41166d8c2af56186e0706111/2025-05/6_5.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        本港地區今日大致多雲，有幾陣驟雨。蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>展望明日初時仍有驟雨，天氣稍涼，最低氣溫在20度左右。星期一天色好轉，日間乾燥。隨後一兩日天氣炎熱，部分時間有陽光，亦有幾陣驟雨。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
