        {
            "title": "響螺角截查小型遊艇遇查揭藏大麻  54歲男舵手涉毒駕被捕",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/7148724bfb35f25bd5bff82b0bbaf70d/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250510/_2025051006120052603.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>昨日（9日）傍晚6時37分，水警北分區人員在赤門海峽響螺角對開約1公里海面執行職務期間，截查經過上址的小型遊艇。經初步調查，54歲姓黃姓舵手未能通過快速口腔液測試，隨後警員在遊艇上檢獲小量懷疑大麻。\n\n</p>\n<p>黃男涉嫌「藏有危險藥物」及「在受指明毒品影響時操作船隻」被捕，他現正被扣留調查，大麻總值仍在點算中。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2068191/即時-港聞-響螺角截查小型遊艇遇查揭藏大麻-54歲男舵手涉毒駕被捕",
